#: ../../sales/amazon_connector/setup.rst:127
msgid ""
"These marketplaces are not officially supported by Odoo - there is no "
"guarantee that adding a new marketplace as described here will work, nor can"
" this be considered as a bug when contacting Odoo Support."
msgstr ""

#: ../../sales/amazon_connector/setup.rst:132
msgid ""
"Amazon marketplaces are only supported in the European and North American "
"region; though Amazon includes Brazil with the North American region and "
"India in the European region, so your mileage may vary; check the `Amazon "
"Documentation "
"<https://docs.developer.amazonservices.com/en_US/dev_guide/DG_Endpoints.html>`_"
" to know to which region your marketplace belongs."
